    "ANOVA analysis on the effects of ESRT showed potential in reducing burnout rates compared with the control group (mean±SD 5.14±2.35 vs 3.14±2.25; p=0.002).",
    "42 SCHC SCHC is a brief form of the mindful self-compassion (MSC) programme used in healthcare.",
    "Both SCHC programmes were led by qualified instructors once a week for 6 weeks and involved several concepts: understanding self-compassion and self-criticism, mindfulness exercises, and tackling stress and burnout.",
    "38, 45 Both SCHC studies reduced burnout scores post-training.",
    "38, 45 Descriptive analysis showed no improvement in DP scores after one of the SCHC programmes."
